r funding an itemized list of other proposed funding sources and the amount requested from each the name and email address of your contact person your organization's assu account number or department's pta place on the cover page incomplete proposals will not be considered you will receive an email acknowledgment upon receipt of your group's proposal shortly after the submission deadline the review committee will meet to discuss each proposal and to make funding decisions you should receive email notification of the committee's decision no later than the seventh week of the quarter funds are typically disbursed five to seven working days after notification questions about the submission process should go to darlene lazar in the school of engineering office of student affairs in 135 huang stay connected itunes icon google+ icon facebook icon twitter icon linkedin icon stanford university school of engineering 475 via ortega stanford california 94305 4121 650.725 1575 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved accreditation info terms of use copyright complaints contact us
